                <li>Add ability to determine user location automatically</li>
                <li>Move change city dialog to context drawer</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="1.2.0" date="2025-09-27">
        <description>
            <p>Responsive Menu Update</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Add various translations</li>
                <li>Fix menu bar for low width screens</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="1.1.4" date="2025-05-09">
        <description>
            <p>Add translations</p>
            <ul>
                <li>Add Portuguese translation</li>
                <li>Add Bulgarian translation</li>
            </ul>
        </description>
    </release>
    <release version="1.1.3" date="2025-05-09">
        <description>
            <p>Add more units</p>
            <ul>
